1) Check Gradle Version            :-   gradle --version
2) Show all Tasks                  :-   gradle task --all
3) Detail about a Task             :-   gradle help --task <task>
4) List of Command-Line Option     :-   gradle --help

1) Run a task                      :-   gradle <task>